If you have any questions or would like to here more about our research, please contact us at andy.woods@xperiment.mobi.
Press escape to leave full screen. You can now close this browser window. Thanks again!
DO NOT FORGET TO ENTER YOUR CODE INTO MECHANICAL TURK."	timeStart="0" width="80%"  align="left" timeEnd="forever" fontSize="20"></addText>

</TRIAL>
  	

</spoken>	


